embed.title: Troops
embed.description:
Troops commonly considered as strong in the current meta

**Front Line**
Peltasts

**Range**
Frost Archers

**Tank**
Yasha, Demon, Meteor Golem, Stone Golem

**Crowd Control**
Pumpkin Guard, Pirate Ship, Rhino Knight

**High-power AoE**
Ballista, Priest Mage

**Back Line Attack**
Magic Apprentice

**Others**
Ghost Assassins, Ice Mage, Undead Soldier, Goblikazes, Taurus Witcher, Voodoo Dolls, Nun
